Deployment Notes:

This project was built with Maven 3.8.1, deployed on Apache Tomcat 10.1.4 and tested on using JUnit 4.


MySQL Database

    This project is supported by a MySQL database running locally on the machine.

    Database dumps are located in src/main/db/. These can imported using MySQL Workbench to create a copy of our database.

    The code is written to connect to the database via JDBC as user: 'root', password: 'iotbay'

    User and pass details can be changed in the DBConnector.java and DBManagerTest.java files.


DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS:

1. Import the database on your machine locally using the database dumps.

2. Start an instance of Apache Tomcat

3. Navigate to the deployment manager tool http://localhost:8080/manager

4. Choose the IoTBay-1.0.war file from this project and deploy on the server.

5.  Go to http://localhost:8080/IoTBay-1.0 to be directed to the IoTBay index page.